# Performance Standards (Beta)

## Core Metrics
```typescript
{
  "performanceStandards": {
    "metrics": {
      "core": {
        "FCP": "< 2.5s",
        "LCP": "< 3.0s"
      }
    },
    "optimization": {
      "images": {
        "formats": ["webp"],
        "loading": "lazy",
        "quality": 80
      },
      "javascript": {
        "bundling": {
          "splitting": true,
          "minification": true
        }
      }
    },
    "caching": {
      "static": {
        "images": "1 month",
        "assets": "1 week"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Removed Features
- Complex monitoring systems
- Advanced image processing
- AI optimizations
- Synthetic testing
- Complex error reporting